=form_tag("#{merge_players_path}", method: :put, style: "margin: 20px auto 0 auto; width: 350px;") do |f|
  .player
    %span Player:
    =select_tag "player", options_from_collection_for_select(@players, "id", "merge_name"), class: 'input-block-level'
  .dupe
    %span Duplicate:
    =select_tag "duplicate", options_from_collection_for_select(@players, "id", "merge_name"), class: 'input-block-level'
  %br
  .info{style:"font-size: 12px;"} Clicking Merge will assign all stat lines and roster spots from the Duplicate to the Player, and delete the Duplicate.
  %br
  %input{type:"submit", value:"Merge", class: 'btn btn-primary btn-block'}